sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: message
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Barbora Waclawikova
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: The iGEM team Groningen 2016 worked on bioencryption in order to safely store data in DNA. In our project we were mainly working with two sequences of DNA which were the encrypted message sequence and the encryption key sequence. The message sequence was created by our software. It is therefore artificial DNA. We ordered the encrypted message sequence as gBlock from IDT (Integrated DNA technologies).
